The purpose of this observational study is the assessment (safety and efficacy) of the St.

 Jude Medical Tendril MRI cent leads.

 The Tendril MRI cent leads are a full part of the Accent MRI cent System, consisting of Tendril MRI cent leads and Accent MRI cent pacemaker.

 The subject population includes patients with a standard bradycardia pacing indication.

